 do this at 10% when I have time.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"xendelaar","CreatedById":139535,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-17T14:50:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223786414\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193921\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221589682085\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022201693\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ralanboyle\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, ralanboyle said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll do this at 10% when I have time.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nReally?! That\u0027s so cool! Maybe I\u0027ll\u00A0 stop my 20% challenge and start a 10% challenge as well!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlease let me know when you\u0027ve started so I can upload your name to the Participants list.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ralanboyle","CreatedById":201693,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-17T17:25:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is a big challenge that will take several videos to make. I\u0027ll start soon but I\u0027ll get side tracked by lots of other small challenges in the mean time. You can put me on the board when I post the first video.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}